Juan Mao swished his tail and approached.
"Did you have fun today?"
Fang asked.
"Woof!"
"Is it fun over there?"
Fang asked again.
Juan Mao jumped up and barked again, wagging his tail vigorously.
"Speak."
"Fun!"
Juan Mao said.
