The Marine Environment Protection Law
"Series on Environmental Protection Knowledge for Adolescents"
The Directory of Marine Wildlife Conservation
"Marine Environmental Management"
"100 Ocean Knowledge that People Must Know in the New Century"
"Oceans, My Home"
